title: Whistleblower Tweet, Missile Strikes in Iraq

description:
Panel guests: Sery Kim, Republican Strategist, Attorney and former Senior Advisor in the Trump Administration and Kevin Walling, Democratic Strategist at HG Creative Media.


Morgan Ortagus, U.S. State Department spokesperson discussed the U.S. missile strikes in Iraq over the weekend.
